            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"part-1-usb-protocoll-libusb-is-your-best-friend\">Part 1 USB-Protocoll: Libusb is your best friend \ud83e\udd17</h2></span>"
